'NPCText\t2222\t\t' + _x("npc conversation", "An untiring servant it is,\ncarrying loads across muddy earth.\nBut one thing that cannot be forced,\nis a return to the place of its birth.") + '\r\n'
'NPCText\t2223\t\t' + _x("npc conversation", "river") + '\r\n'
'NPCText\t2224\t\t' + _x("npc conversation", "With sharp edged wit,\nAnd pointed poise,\nIt can settle disputes,\nWithout a noise.") + '\r\n'
